title: MNAs calls on PM
content:
ISLAMABAD, Feb 28 (APP): Members of National Assembly separately called on Prime Minister Shehbaz Sharif here on Tuesday and discussed various matters.
Those who met the prime minister include MNA Saad Waseem, MNA Chaudhary Faqir Ahmed, and MNA Chaudhary Zulfiqar Bhinder.
The matters relating to constituencies of the MNAs also came under discussion.
